  "remarks": "Gas pipeline construction company owned or controlled by Arkady Rotenberg.  Rotenberg created SGM Group in 2008 after acquiring multiple Gazprom contractors.\nSGM Group won a major tender for the construction of the Kerch bridge that links Crimea to mainland Russia.\nRegistration ID: 1027800000084 (Russia)\nGovernment Gazette Number: 09804148 (Russia)\nTax ID No.: 7831000122 (Russia) Email: info@ooosgm.ru\nWebsite: www.ooosgm.com ; www.ooosgm.ru; Listing: Listed on 16 June 2017, re-listed 10 Jun 2020 and 29 March 2021 and 10 June 2023",
